headline: 3 Reasons to Sell BIIB and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: The past six months have been a windfall for Biogen’s shareholders. The company’s stock price has jumped 41.7%, setting a new 52-week high of $188.65 per share. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
